---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import Container from "@/components/Container.astro";
import hostBrian from "@/assets/host-brian.jpg";
---

<Container class="max-w-4xl">
  <h2 class="mb-10">About the organizers</h2>
  <div class="grid gap-10 md:grid-cols-2">
    <div class="flex gap-5">
      <Image
        src={hostBrian}
        alt="Brian, host"
        width={128}
        class="h-16 w-16 shrink-0 rounded-full border border-accent object-cover"
      />
      <div>
        <h3 class="mb-2">
          Brian <span class="text-lg text-accent">/ Host</span>
        </h3>
        <p class="italic">
          I created Flirt Improv because the world could use more love and joy,
          and the fun kind of sparks! Improv classes and other events taught me
          that people light up when they feel safe to experiment and be
          unexpected, and flirting is just spicy play for grown-ups. I believe
          in fostering the kind of electric connections that give you
          butterflies and make life worth living. Let's create a space for fun,
          authenticity, and sizzle!
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="flex gap-5">
      <div
        class="flex h-16 w-16 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-dashed border-accent font-display text-2xl text-accent"
      >
        ?
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="mb-2">
          Co-host <span class="text-lg">/ coming soon</span>
        </h3>
        <p>
          A second organizer is joining the fun. Their introduction will land
          here soon.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Container>
